{"snp3.4:0.1":"Sutta Nipata 3.4 ","snp3.4:0.2":"Puralasa (sundarikabharadvaja) sutta ","snp3.4:1.1":"Evam me sutam—","snp3.4:1.2":"ekam samayam bhagava kosalesu viharati sundarikaya nadiya tire. ","snp3.4:1.3":"Tena kho pana samayena sundarikabharadvajo brahmano sundarikaya nadiya tire aggim juhati, aggihuttam paricarati. ","snp3.4:1.4":"Atha kho sundarikabharadvajo brahmano aggim juhitva aggihuttam paricaritva utthayasana samanta catuddisa anuvilokesi: ","snp3.4:1.5":"“ko nu kho imam habyasesam bhunjeyya”ti? ","snp3.4:1.6":"Addasa kho sundarikabharadvajo brahmano bhagavantam avidure annatarasmim rukkhamule sasisam parutam nisinnam; ","snp3.4:1.7":"disvana vamena hatthena habyasesam gahetva dakkhinena hatthena kamandalum gahetva yena bhagava tenupasankami. ","snp3.4:2.1":"Atha kho bhagava sundarikabharadvajassa brahmanassa padasaddena sisam vivari. ","snp3.4:2.2":"Atha kho sundarikabharadvajo brahmano: “mundo ayam bhavam, mundako ayam bhavan”ti tatova puna nivattitukamo ahosi. ","snp3.4:2.3":"Atha kho sundarikabharadvajassa brahmanassa etadahosi: ","snp3.4:2.4":"“mundapi hi idhekacce brahmana bhavanti, yannunaham upasankamitva jatim puccheyyan”ti. ","snp3.4:2.5":"Atha kho sundarikabharadvajo brahmano yena bhagava tenupasankami; upasankamitva bhagavantam etadavoca: ","snp3.4:2.6":"“kimjacco bhavan”ti? ","snp3.4:3.1":"Atha kho bhagava sundarikabharadvajam brahmanam gathahi ajjhabhasi: ","snp3.4:4.1":"“Na brahmano nomhi na rajaputto, ","snp3.4:4.2":"Na vessayano uda koci nomhi; ","snp3.4:4.3":"Gottam parinnaya puthujjananam, ","snp3.4:4.4":"Akincano manta carami loke. ","snp3.4:5.1":"Sanghativasi agaho carami, ","snp3.4:5.2":"Nivuttakeso abhinibbutatto; ","snp3.4:5.3":"Alippamano idha manavehi, ","snp3.4:5.4":"Akallam mam brahmana pucchasi gottapanham”. ","snp3.4:6.1":"“Pucchanti ve bho brahmana brahmanebhi, ","snp3.4:6.2":"Saha brahmano no bhavan”ti. ","snp3.4:7.1":"“Brahmano hi ce tvam brusi, ","snp3.4:7.2":"Manca brusi abrahmanam; ","snp3.4:7.3":"Tam tam savittim pucchami, ","snp3.4:7.4":"Tipadam catuvisatakkharam”. ","snp3.4:8.1":"“Kim nissita isayo manuja, ","snp3.4:8.2":"Khattiya brahmana devatanam; ","snp3.4:8.3":"Yannamakappayimsu puthu idha loke”. ","snp3.4:9.1":"“Yadantagu vedagu yannakale, ","snp3.4:9.2":"Yassahutim labhe tassijjheti brumi”. ","snp3.4:10.1":"“Addha hi tassa hutamijjhe, ","snp3.4:10.2":"(iti brahmano) ","snp3.4:10.3":"Yam tadisam vedagumaddasama; ","snp3.4:10.4":"Tumhadisananhi adassanena, ","snp3.4:10.5":"Anno jano bhunjati puralasam”. ","snp3.4:11.1":"“Tasmatiha tvam brahmana atthena, ","snp3.4:11.2":"Atthiko upasankamma puccha; ","snp3.4:11.3":"Santam vidhumam anigham nirasam, ","snp3.4:11.4":"Appevidha abhivinde sumedham”. ","snp3.4:12.1":"“Yanne ratoham bho gotama, ","snp3.4:12.2":"Yannam yitthukamo naham pajanami; ","snp3.4:12.3":"Anusasatu mam bhavam, ","snp3.4:12.4":"Yattha hutam ijjhate bruhi me tam”. ","snp3.4:13.1":"“Tena hi tvam, brahmana, odahassu sotam; dhammam te desessami—","snp3.4:14.1":"Ma jatim pucchi carananca puccha, ","snp3.4:14.2":"Kattha have jayati jatavedo; ","snp3.4:14.3":"Nicakulinopi muni dhitima, ","snp3.4:14.4":"Ajaniyo hoti hirinisedho. ","snp3.4:15.1":"Saccena danto damasa upeto, ","snp3.4:15.2":"Vedantagu vusitabrahmacariyo; ","snp3.4:15.3":"Kalena tamhi habyam pavecche, ","snp3.4:15.4":"Yo brahmano punnapekkho yajetha. ","snp3.4:16.1":"Ye kame hitva agaha caranti, ","snp3.4:16.2":"Susannatatta tasaramva ujjum; ","snp3.4:16.3":"Kalena tesu habyam pavecche, ","snp3.4:16.4":"Yo brahmano punnapekkho yajetha. ","snp3.4:17.1":"Ye vitaraga susamahitindriya, ","snp3.4:17.2":"Candova rahuggahana pamutta; ","snp3.4:17.3":"Kalena tesu habyam pavecche, ","snp3.4:17.4":"Yo brahmano punnapekkho yajetha. ","snp3.4:18.1":"Asajjamana vicaranti loke, ","snp3.4:18.2":"Sada sata hitva mamayitani; ","snp3.4:18.3":"Kalena tesu habyam pavecche, ","snp3.4:18.4":"Yo brahmano punnapekkho yajetha. ","snp3.4:19.1":"Yo kame hitva abhibhuyyacari, ","snp3.4:19.2":"Yo vedi jatimaranassa antam; ","snp3.4:19.3":"Parinibbuto udakarahadova sito, ","snp3.4:19.4":"Tathagato arahati puralasam. ","snp3.4:20.1":"Samo samehi visamehi dure, ","snp3.4:20.2":"Tathagato hoti anantapanno; ","snp3.4:20.3":"Anupalitto idha va huram va, ","snp3.4:20.4":"Tathagato arahati puralasam. ","snp3.4:21.1":"Yamhi na maya vasati na mano, ","snp3.4:21.2":"Yo vitalobho amamo niraso; ","snp3.4:21.3":"Panunnakodho abhinibbutatto, ","snp3.4:21.4":"Yo brahmano sokamalam ahasi; ","snp3.4:21.5":"Tathagato arahati puralasam. ","snp3.4:22.1":"Nivesanam yo manaso ahasi, ","snp3.4:22.2":"Pariggaha yassa na santi keci; ","snp3.4:22.3":"Anupadiyano idha va huram va, ","snp3.4:22.4":"Tathagato arahati puralasam. ","snp3.4:23.1":"Samahito yo udatari ogham, ","snp3.4:23.2":"Dhammam cannasi paramaya ditthiya; ","snp3.4:23.3":"Khinasavo antimadehadhari, ","snp3.4:23.4":"Tathagato arahati puralasam. ","snp3.4:24.1":"Bhavasava yassa vaci khara ca, ","snp3.4:24.2":"Vidhupita atthagata na santi; ","snp3.4:24.3":"Sa vedagu sabbadhi vippamutto, ","snp3.4:24.4":"Tathagato arahati puralasam. ","snp3.4:25.1":"Sangatigo yassa na santi sanga, ","snp3.4:25.2":"Yo manasattesu amanasatto; ","snp3.4:25.3":"Dukkham parinnaya sakhettavatthum, ","snp3.4:25.4":"Tathagato arahati puralasam. ","snp3.4:26.1":"Asam anissaya vivekadassi, ","snp3.4:26.2":"Paravediyam ditthimupativatto; ","snp3.4:26.3":"Arammana yassa na santi keci, ","snp3.4:26.4":"Tathagato arahati puralasam. ","snp3.4:27.1":"Paropara yassa samecca dhamma, ","snp3.4:27.2":"Vidhupita atthagata na santi; ","snp3.4:27.3":"Santo upadanakhaye vimutto, ","snp3.4:27.4":"Tathagato arahati puralasam. ","snp3.4:28.1":"Samyojanam jatikhayantadassi, ","snp3.4:28.2":"Yopanudi ragapatham asesam; ","snp3.4:28.3":"Suddho nidoso vimalo akaco, ","snp3.4:28.4":"Tathagato arahati puralasam. ","snp3.4:29.1":"Yo attano attanam nanupassati, ","snp3.4:29.2":"Samahito ujjugato thitatto; ","snp3.4:29.3":"Sa ve anejo akhilo akankho, ","snp3.4:29.4":"Tathagato arahati puralasam. ","snp3.4:30.1":"Mohantara yassa na santi keci, ","snp3.4:30.2":"Sabbesu dhammesu ca nanadassi; ","snp3.4:30.3":"Sariranca antimam dhareti, ","snp3.4:30.4":"Patto ca sambodhimanuttaram sivam; ","snp3.4:30.5":"Ettavata yakkhassa suddhi, ","snp3.4:30.6":"Tathagato arahati puralasam”. ","snp3.4:31.1":"“Hutanca mayham hutamatthu saccam, ","snp3.4:31.2":"Yam tadisam vedagunam alattham; ","snp3.4:31.3":"Brahma hi sakkhi patiganhatu me bhagava, ","snp3.4:31.4":"Bhunjatu me bhagava puralasam”. ","snp3.4:32.1":"“Gathabhigitam me abhojaneyyam, ","snp3.4:32.2":"Sampassatam brahmana nesa dhammo; ","snp3.4:32.3":"Gathabhigitam panudanti buddha, ","snp3.4:32.4":"Dhamme sati brahmana vuttiresa. ","snp3.4:33.1":"Annena ca kevalinam mahesim, ","snp3.4:33.2":"Khinasavam kukkuccavupasantam; ","snp3.4:33.3":"Annena panena upatthahassu, ","snp3.4:33.4":"Khettanhi tam punnapekkhassa hoti”. ","snp3.4:34.1":"“Sadhaham bhagava tatha vijannam, ","snp3.4:34.2":"Yo dakkhinam bhunjeyya madisassa; ","snp3.4:34.3":"Yam yannakale pariyesamano, ","snp3.4:34.4":"Pappuyya tava sasanam”. ","snp3.4:35.1":"“Sarambha yassa vigata, ","snp3.4:35.2":"Cittam yassa anavilam; ","snp3.4:35.3":"Vippamutto ca kamehi, ","snp3.4:35.4":"Thinam yassa panuditam. ","snp3.4:36.1":"Simantanam vinetaram, ","snp3.4:36.2":"Jatimaranakovidam; ","snp3.4:36.3":"Munim moneyyasampannam, ","snp3.4:36.4":"Tadisam yannamagatam. ","snp3.4:37.1":"Bhakutim vinayitvana, ","snp3.4:37.2":"Panjalika namassatha; ","snp3.4:37.3":"Pujetha annapanena, ","snp3.4:37.4":"Evam ijjhanti dakkhina”. ","snp3.4:38.1":"“Buddho bhavam arahati puralasam, ","snp3.4:38.2":"Punnakhettamanuttaram; ","snp3.4:38.3":"Ayago sabbalokassa, ","snp3.4:38.4":"Bhoto dinnam mahapphalan”ti. ","snp3.4:39.1":"Atha kho sundarikabharadvajo brahmano bhagavantam etadavoca: ","snp3.4:39.2":"“abhikkantam, bho gotama, abhikkantam, bho gotama. ","snp3.4:39.3":"Seyyathapi, bho gotama, nikkujjitam va ukkujjeyya, paticchannam va vivareyya, mulhassa va maggam acikkheyya, andhakare va telapajjotam dhareyya: ‘cakkhumanto rupani dakkhanti’ti; evamevam bhota gotamena anekapariyayena dhammo pakasito. ","snp3.4:39.4":"Esaham bhavantam gotamam saranam gacchami dhammanca bhikkhusanghanca. ","snp3.4:39.5":"Labheyyaham bhoto gotamassa santike pabbajjam, labheyyam upasampadan”ti. ","snp3.4:39.6":"Alattha kho sundarikabharadvajo brahmano …pe… ","snp3.4:39.7":"arahatam ahositi. ","snp3.4:39.8":"Sundarikabharadvajasuttam catuttham. "}